name: THE TICKLE - Issue #33 Mihai Grecu Special Edition
description:
Special 1/1 edition of Issue #33. Art zine focused on Hic et Nunc artists and writers.

Issue #33 features artists Mihai Grecu (@the_grecu), Andreas Rau (@andreasrau_eu) & Paul Prudence (@kazuhiroaihara), with an AI poetry collaboration between Guadalupe Sierra (@sierra_guada) & Sudowrite (@sudowrite)

Created by artist Wily Guys (@guyswily) with help from Theo Horsmeier (@THorsmeier) and Joanne Rush (@JonicolaRush).
